com.moblima.user

Class MovieGoer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.moblima.user.User
      • com.moblima.user.MovieGoer

  • public class MovieGoer
extends com.moblima.user.User
    MovieGoer is an entity class which extends from the generalized User entity. Its main purpose is to differentiate between a admin in order to perform the standard MovieGoer functions. Next to that the moviegoer class can in future expension of the program be used to store more information regarding to the moviegoer object, for Example: user seat preferences could be stored or creditcard details can be saved to make payments faster.

    Ivo Janssen
